\v 13 Uchatsika pamusoro peshumba nechiva;
\s Mwana weshumba nenyoka uchazvitsikirira pasi.
\p
\v 14 "Zvaakandida, ndichamurwira; Ndichamuisa pakakwirira, nokuti wakaziva zita rangu.
