\v 15 Iye achadana kwandiri, ndichamupindura;
\s .Ini ndichava naye pakutambudzika; Ndichamurwira, nokumukudza.
\p
\v 16 Ndichamugutsa noupenyu hurefu, Nokumuratidza ruponeso rwangu."
